Gossip Girl star Kelly Rutherford has lost residential custody of her two children to ex-husband Daniel Giersch, according to a new report.

The 43-year-old actress is said to be 'devastated' after a judge ruled her five-year-old son and three-year-old daughter can remain with their father in France, where he currently resides.

Rutherford was fighting the 37-year-old German businessman in family court to bring her children back to the U.S.

